{"word":"G1342 - δίκαιος - díkaios - dik'-ah-yos - Just","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δίκαιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">díkaios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dik'-ah-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Just</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நீதிமானாயிருக்கிற, நீதியுள்ள, நியாயமான, உண்மையுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"righteous, observing divine and human laws; one who is such as he ought to be"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1349 - δίκη - díkē - dee'-kay/1349\">G1349</a>; <i>equitable</i> (in character or act); by implication <i>innocent</i>, <i>holy</i> (absolutely or relatively): - just, meet, right (-eous).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1341/1341\">G1341</a>, <a href=\"#/G1342/1342\">G1342</a>, <a href=\"#/G1343/1343\">G1343</a>, <a href=\"#/G1344/1344\">G1344</a>, <a href=\"#/G1345/1345\">G1345</a>, <a href=\"#/G1346/1346\">G1346</a>, <a href=\"#/G1347/1347\">G1347</a>, <a href=\"#/G1349/1349\">G1349</a>"}]}